Dia. 01 Five Space Shape
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is a powerful vital point which increases the eye-space.
\par However, in this situation, after White 2 Black can't live.
\par
\par After Black 3, White 4 is the vital point and it becomes the dead five space shape.
\par If Black plays at 4 instead of 3, White takes it with A and Black is dead again.
\par
\par
\par }
