Dia. 03 Black can't Live with 1
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is also the 1-2 point.
\par Is it possible to live with this move?
\par
\par White 2 is the vital point. After Black 3 White 4 is another vital point. It became the same shape like in Dia. 01.
\par
\par So it is not possible to live with Black 1 either.
\par
\par
\par }
