Dia. 04 Vital Point of Living
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black has no other way but to play the last 1-2 point at 1.
\par After White 2, it is good to expand the eye-space with 3.
\par
\par Black lived up to 5. It is good that Black has two outside liberties.
\par }
