Dia. 05 White 1?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Against Black \'a1\'e3, it is not scary if White plays at 1.
\par Black can live with 2.
\par
\par Next, if White takes it with A, Black plays dansu from B and White can't connect.
\par
\par Black can play at B instead of 2, the result is going to be the same.
\par
\par
\par }
